        "excerpt": "Not sure where to start? Here's a quick guide to downloading and setting up a bookmark organizer that won't let you down.",
        "content": "\n# Download a Reliable Bookmark Organizer\n\nYou've decided you need a better bookmark system. Now what?\n\nDownloading and setting up a bookmark organizer should take five minutes, not an afternoon of research.\n\n## The Fastest Path to Better Bookmarks\n\n1. Visit [markify.tech](https://markify.tech)\n2. Install the browser extension for your browser\n3. Import your existing bookmarks (optional)\n4. Start saving with one click\n\nThat's it. Seriously.\n\n## What to Look For in Any Tool\n\n**Browser extension.** If you can't save from your browser with one click, you won't use it.\n\n**Cloud sync.** Your bookmarks should follow you across devices.\n\n**Search.** If you can't find what you saved, there's no point in saving.\n\n**Active development.** Check when the last update was. Abandoned tools are security risks.\n\n## What to Avoid\n\n- Tools that haven't been updated in 12+ months\n- Extensions with excessive permissions\n- Services with no privacy policy\n- \"Free\" tools with no clear business model\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### Is Markify free?\nYes. Generous free tier. Premium adds advanced features.\n\n### Do I need to create an account?\nYes, for sync. But setup takes 30 seconds.\n\n### Can I try it before committing?\nAbsolutely. Install, try for a week with the free tier. No payment info required.\n    ",
